msgstr "After enabling, 2.4G and 5G will use the same name, and the router will automatically select the best Wi-Fi network for devices. If close to the router, it will switch to 5G; otherwise, it will switch to 2.4G. However, due to differences in terminal devices, issues may arise such as brief network interruption during automatic signal source switching or even frequent disconnections."

